# Branding

Follow [BRANDING.md](../../BRANDING.md) for all visual and motion work.

## Non-negotiables

- **Quiet luxury:** mist paper, ink, sage, gold accent — no purple, neon, emoji, or “Portfolio” labels
- **Hero stays unique:** full-bleed portrait, oversized name lockup, `--hero` exit parallax, ken-burns — do not reuse in body sections
- **Body sections:** contained layouts, gold eyebrow + display title, soft washes, entry reveals only
- Prefer CSS-only motion; honor `prefers-reduced-motion`
- Extend existing tokens in `src/styles/global.css`; update `BRANDING.md` if the system changes
